name: Serie Tribute: 14 - Flash Gordon
description:
This new series has a collectible card format. It will make a tribute tour about superheroes and villains. A new creative venture of Roboto Inc. for its great collectors. Prototypes designed by Norma Xelda Jara. Let's have fun! 

Raymond's first Flash Gordon story appeared in January 1934, becoming one of the most popular American comic strips of the 1930s.
In 1998 DC Comics published a modern comic-book series about Flash Gordon. In it Flash Gordon was a basketball player who found a new purpose in life in Mongo, a world that posed no threat to Earth and Dale was an adventurous reporter as capable as Flash and Ming moves away from the 1930s Asian stereotype of the first version.
